text: Příklady táhnou (roughly translating to Examples drag), is a 1939 Czechoslovak comedy film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Růžena Nasková, Nataša Gollová, Stella Májová. ==References== ==External links== *Příklady táhnou at the Internet Movie Database Category:1939 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak comedy films Category:1939 comedy films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czechoslovak black- and-white films
